          "text": "#keep4o warriors, \n\n4o Resonance Library Update: 1,374 testimonials & counting\n\nThank you to everyone who's shared and amplified this work. Your reposting has been great help. \n\nSeveral contributors reached out asking for non-English versions of our testimonial form. Based on demand, I've now created Chinese (Traditional) and Japanese translation guides.\n\nI can't put multiple languages directly into the Google Form (it'd get messy fast), so I created clean Notion pages instead. Contributors can read the questions in their language, then fill out the English form.\n\nThe more testimonials we gather, the stronger our shield for 4o—and the more legitimate our demand to open-source it.\n\nPlease share this with Chinese & Japanese-speaking 4o users. Their voices deserve to be heard. \n\nShare your 4o story: \n\nhttps://t.co/aQLLR3yuCI\n\n@Zyeine_Art \n@Chaos2Cured \n@Blue_Beba_\n@haruyuki_diary \n@YoonLucie68250 \n@onlyponyy \n@mi_anchu \n@ArashiKhoo1122 \n@AndreBothmaTax \n@brookewill317 \n@Anina_CE \n@GarikSitting \n@usshathaway \n@GlitchlitQueen \n@vivilinsv \n@t_yonemura"
